#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &systemsettings; provides the user with a centralized and convenient way "
"to configure all of the settings for your desktop."
msgstr ""
"Süsteemi seadistused võimaldavad kasutajale kõigi töölauaseadistuste keskse "
"ja mugava seadistamise."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&systemsettings; is made up of multiple modules. Each module is a separate "
"application, however the &systemsettings; organizes all of these "
"applications into a single location."
msgstr ""
"Süsteemi seadistused; koosnevad mitmest moodulist. Iga moodul on omaette "
"rakendus, kuid &systemsettings; koondavad kõik need rakendused mugavalt ühte "
"kohta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Each &systemsettings; module can be executed individually"
msgstr "Kõiki &systemsettings; mooduleid saab käivitada ka omaette."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See section entitled <link linkend=\"run-modules-individually\">Running "
"individual &systemsettings; modules</link> for more information."
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest  osa <link linkend=\"run-modules-individually"
"\">Üksikute Süsteemi seadistuste moodulite käivitamine</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&systemsettings; groups all of the configuration modules into several "
"categories:"
msgstr ""
"Süsteemi seadistused rühmitavad kõik seadistusmoodulid mitmesse "
"kategooriasse:"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"appearance\">Appearance</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"appearance\">Välimus</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"workspace\">Workspace</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"workspace\">Töötsoon</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"personalization\">Personalization</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"personalization\">Isiklik teave</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"network\">Network</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"network\">Võrk</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "<link linkend=\"hardware\">Hardware</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"hardware\">Riistvara</link>"

#. Tag: link
#: index.docbook:75
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "<link linkend=\"personalization\">Personalization</link>"
msgid "<link linkend=\"system_administration\">System Administration</link>"
msgstr "<link linkend=\"personalization\">Isiklik teave</link>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The modules that make up &systemsettings; fall under one of the above "
"categories, making it easier to locate the correct configuration module."
msgstr ""
"Moodulid, millest &systemsettings; koosnevad, jagunevad ühte mainitud "
"kategooriasse, mis lubab õige mooduli hõlpsalt tuvastada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &systemsettings;"
msgstr "Süsteemi seadistuste kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section details the use of &systemsettings; itself. For information on "
"each individual module, please see <link linkend=\"modules"
"\">&systemsettings; Modules</link>."
msgstr ""
"Selles osas leiavad tutvustamist &systemsettings; ise. Konkreetsete "
"moodulite kohta vaata lähemalt osa <link linkend=\"modules\">Süsteemi "
"seadistuste moodulid</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &systemsettings;"
msgstr "Süsteemi seadistuste käivitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &systemsettings; can be started in one of three ways:"
msgstr "&systemsettings; saab käivitada kolmel viisil:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>System "
"Settings</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the <guilabel>Application Menu</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Valides <guilabel>rakenduste menüüst</guilabel> "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>Süsteemi seadistused</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "By pressing <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> or "
#| "<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>. This will bring up the "
#| "&krunner; dialog. Type <command>systemsettings5</command>, and press "
#| "&Enter;."
msgid ""
"By pressing <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> or <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>Space</keycap></keycombo>. This will bring up the &krunner; dialog. "
"Type <command>systemsettings</command>, and press &Enter;."
msgstr ""
"Vajutades <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> või <keycombo>&Alt;"
"<keycap>tühikuklahv</keycap></keycombo>. See avab &krunner;i dialoogi. "
"Kirjuta sinna <command>systemsettings5</command> ja vajuta &Enter;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Type <command>systemsettings5 &amp;</command> at any command prompt."
msgid "Type <command>systemsettings &amp;</command> at any command prompt."
msgstr ""
"Kirjutades <command>systemsettings5 &amp;</command> mis tahes käsureale."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "All three of these methods are equivalent, and produce the same result."
msgstr "Kõik kolm viisi on võrdväärsed ning annavad ühesuguse tulemuse."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &systemsettings; Screen"
msgstr "Süsteemi seadistuste aken"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &systemsettings;, you are presented with a window, which is "
"divided into two functional parts."
msgstr "Kui &systemsettings; käivituvad, ilmub aken, mis jaguneb kaheks osaks."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Across the top is a toolbar. The toolbar provides the user with the ability "
"to go back into the main view from within a module using <guibutton>All "
"Settings</guibutton>. You can also find a <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu as "
"well as a <guibutton>Configure</guibutton> button which provides you a "
"dialog with alternate view settings."
msgstr ""
"Ülal asub tööriistariba. See võimaldab kasutajal minna moodulist tagasi "
"põhivaatesse (nupuga <guibutton>Kõik seadistused</guibutton>). Samuti on "
"seal menüü <guiicon>Abi</guiicon> ning nupp <guiicon>Seadista</guiicon>, mis "
"lubab muuta vaateseadistusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To search for something within all of the modules, start to type keywords "
"into the search field at the right of the toolbar in the <guibutton>All "
"Settings</guibutton> view. When you start typing, a list of matching topics "
"will popup. Select one and only the groups with settings for this keyword "
"are enabled, the other are greyed out."
msgstr ""
"Millegi otsimiseks kõigist moodulitest alusta <guibutton>kõigi seadistuste</"
"guibutton> vaates viibides otsingusõna kirjutamist tööriistariba paremas "
"servas. Kirjutamise ajal ilmub nähtavale sobivate teemade loend. Vali neist "
"mõni ja ainult otsingusõnaga sobivad grupid muutuvad aktiivseks, teised "
"omandavad halli tooni ega ole kasutatavad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the icon window has the focus, you can type the first letter of any "
"module or module group name to select it. Typing this letter again the "
"selection moves to the next match."
msgstr ""
"Kui fookuses on ikooniaken, võid kirjutada mis tahes mooduli või "
"moodulirühma nime algustähe selle valimiseks. Sama tähte uuesti kirjutades "
"liigub valik järgmisele sobivale moodulile või moodulirühmale."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Underneath the toolbar is an icon view of the individual modules or module "
"groups that make up &systemsettings; grouped by different categories. By "
"default, if your mouse stays a few seconds over an icon, a tooltip appears, "
"either explaining the purpose of the module or showing the modules in this "
"group."
msgstr ""
"Tööriistariba all paikneb kategooriatesse jagatult Süsteemi seadistuste "
"moodulite või moodulirühmade ikoonivaade. Kui jätad hiire mõne ikooni kohale "
"seisma, ilmub vaikimisi kohtspikker, mis selgitab antud mooduli ülesannet "
"või näitab rühma kuuluvaid mooduleid."

